@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oafctc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 - wp.exp((tmp + 0.14 + v1 + 0.41)))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.60)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = wp.exp((v0 * v2))
    v2 = 0.66
    tmp = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.06 / tmp + 0.77) - 0.27))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
